---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="UU MEMO - 紀錄生活碎隙">
    <Header />

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16">
            <!-- Left Content Area (Main) -->
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-20">
                <!-- 最新文章 (Horizontal Cards) -->
                <section>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight border-b-2 border-uu-main pb-1"
                        >
                            最新文章
                        </h2>
                        <span
                            class="text-xs opacity-40 font-mono tracking-widest"
                            >LATEST UPDATES</span
                        >
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Horizontal Card 1 -->
                        <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 group">
                            <a
                                href="/posts/first-post"
                                class="w-full md:w-72 aspect-[16/10] bg-uu-sub/30 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shrink-0 block"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="w-full h-full bg-[#eaddce] flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main/20"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl"
                                        >image</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                                <div
                                    class="text-[10px] tracking-widest text-uu-main/60 mb-2 font-medium flex items-center gap-1"
                                >
                                    <span>2026.02.12</span> /
                                    <a
                                        href="/category/life"
                                        class="hover:text-uu-main hover:underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 transition-colors"
                                        >生活記事</a
                                    >
                                </div>
                                <h3
                                    class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-uu-dark transition-colors"
                                >
                                    <a href="/posts/first-post"
                                        >在城市的夾縫中尋找陽光，關於春天的第一次散步</a
                                    >
                                </h3>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 line-clamp-2 mb-4"
                                >
                                    清晨的空氣還帶著一絲涼意，但路邊的櫻花枝頭已經隱約可見飽滿的芽。這是我來到這個城市的第三個春天，依然對這些微小的變化感到驚喜...
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <div class="h-px bg-uu-sub/50 w-full"></div>

                        <!-- Horizontal Card 2 (日文範例) -->
                        <article
                            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 group"
                            lang="ja"
                        >
                            <a
                                href="/posts/tokyo-cafe"
                                class="w-full md:w-72 aspect-[16/10] bg-uu-sub/30 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shrink-0 block"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="w-full h-full bg-[#e6ded5] flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main/20"
                                >
                                    <span
                                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl"
                                        >image</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                                <div
                                    class="text-[10px] tracking-widest text-uu-main/60 mb-2 font-medium flex items-center gap-1"
                                >
                                    <span>2026.01.28</span> /
                                    <a
                                        href="/category/life"
                                        class="hover:text-uu-main hover:underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 transition-colors"
                                        >日本生活</a
                                    >
                                </div>
                                <h3
                                    class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-uu-dark transition-colors"
                                >
                                    <a href="/posts/tokyo-cafe"
                                        >東京の静かな午後、古い喫茶店で見つけた物語。</a
                                    >
                                </h3>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 line-clamp-2 mb-4"
                                >
                                    神保町の裏通りにある小さな喫茶店。そこには、時間が止まったような静寂がありました。一杯のコーヒーと、誰かが残した古い本...
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 text-right">
                        <a
                            href="/posts"
                            class="btn-text text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-uu-main/80 hover:text-uu-main"
                            >看所有文章 →</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- 精選文章 (Vertical Cards) -->
                <section>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-8">
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight border-b-2 border-uu-main pb-1"
                        >
                            精選文章
                        </h2>
                        <span
                            class="text-xs opacity-40 font-mono tracking-widest"
                            >FEATURED POSTS</span
                        >
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <!-- Vertical Card 1 -->
                        <article
                            class="bg-uu-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-uu-sub group shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
                        >
                            <a href="/posts/first-post">
                                <div
                                    class="aspect-[16/9] bg-uu-sub/20 relative"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main/20"
                                    >
                                        <span
                                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl"
                                            >photo_library</span
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <div class="p-6">
                                <h3
                                    class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-uu-dark transition-colors"
                                >
                                    <a href="/posts/first-post"
                                        >那些年我們一起讀過的詩集：關於孤獨與陪伴</a
                                    >
                                </h3>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm opacity-70 line-clamp-3 mb-6 leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    書架上的那本詩集已經有些發黃，但每一次翻開，都能在字裡行間找到當時的自己。詩不是為了解答生活，而是為了安慰靈魂。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <!-- Vertical Card 2 -->
                        <article
                            class="bg-uu-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-uu-sub group shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"
                        >
                            <a href="/posts/first-post">
                                <div
                                    class="aspect-[16/9] bg-uu-sub/20 relative"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-uu-main/20"
                                    >
                                        <span
                                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl"
                                            >photo_library</span
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                            <div class="p-6">
                                <h3
                                    class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-uu-dark transition-colors"
                                >
                                    <a href="/posts/first-post"
                                        >給未來的自己：在繁瑣日常中保持溫度的五個練習</a
                                    >
                                </h3>
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm opacity-70 line-clamp-3 mb-6 leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    生活是由無數個微小的瞬間組成的。如何從瑣事中抽離，看見隱藏在日常之下的光？這是我給自己設計的五個生活練習。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 text-right">
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=精選"
                            class="btn-text text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-uu-main/80 hover:text-uu-main"
                            >看所有精選 →</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Sidebar -->
            <aside class="w-full lg:w-72 space-y-12 shrink-0">
                <!-- Author Bio -->
                <section
                    class="bg-uu-light p-8 rounded-2xl border border-uu-sub text-center"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-uu-sub/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/uu-memo.png"
                            alt="UU Avatar"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">UU</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs opacity-60 mb-6 tracking-widest">
                        WRITER / TRAVELER
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80 mb-6">
                        在東京與台北之間生活。喜歡底片攝影、黑咖啡以及安靜的書寫時光。
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                        <a
                            href="mailto:uu-memo@outlook.com"
                            class="text-uu-main/50 hover:text-uu-main transition-colors"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
                        </a>
                        <a
                            href="#"
                            class="text-uu-main/50 hover:text-uu-main transition-colors"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                >alternate_email</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Directory (Sitemap Index) -->
                <section>
                    <h4
                        class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest border-b border-uu-sub pb-2 mb-6 uppercase"
                    >
                        目錄索引
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium">
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/category/life"
                                class="flex items-center justify-between group"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >日常紀錄</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm opacity-30"
                                    >chevron_right</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/category/reading"
                                class="flex items-center justify-between group"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >讀書筆記</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm opacity-30"
                                    >chevron_right</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/category/travel"
                                class="flex items-center justify-between group"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >旅行見聞</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm opacity-30"
                                    >chevron_right</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/category/visual"
                                class="flex items-center justify-between group"
                            >
                                <span
                                    class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >影像生活</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm opacity-30"
                                    >chevron_right</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <!-- Tag Cloud (Optional decoration) -->
                <section>
                    <h4
                        class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest border-b border-uu-sub pb-2 mb-6 uppercase"
                    >
                        熱門標籤
                    </h4>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=咖啡"
                            class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >#咖啡</a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=東京"
                            class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >#東京</a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=底片"
                            class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >#底片</a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=隨筆"
                            class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >#隨筆</a
                        >
                        <a
                            href="/posts?tag=閱讀"
                            class="text-[11px] px-3 py-1 bg-uu-sub/20 rounded-full hover:bg-uu-main hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                            >#閱讀</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </section>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
